main.rs → Starts the server, wires up routes, middleware, config.

config/ → Loads settings (from .env via dotenvy or config crate).

routes/ → Maps endpoints like /api/users, /api/auth.

handlers/ → Contains async functions that handle requests.

models/ → Request/response structs, DB schema models (can be used with serde).

db/ → Connection pool setup (e.g., with sqlx or diesel).

utils/ → Reusable helpers (JWT auth, password hashing, etc.).

errors.rs → Custom error enum (integrates with actix_web::ResponseError).